+**Step 6: Implement `evaluate_acceptance()`**
+
+MVP rules:
+
+- `transcript_coverage`
+  - pass if at least one success criterion has meaningful lexical overlap with final response or evidence text
+  - inconclusive if final response is empty or too vague
+- `tool_evidence`
+  - pass if completion is claimed and at least one relevant tool message exists
+  - inconclusive if completion is claimed but no tool evidence exists
+  - pass if no completion claim is made and the task is clearly presented as partial
+
+Final status rule:
+- any required fail -> `fail`
+- else any inconclusive -> `inconclusive`
+- else `pass`
